Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Does every animal have their\Ncopy of "Wuthering Hooves"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! I love Furry\NFriends Book Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's discuss\Nthe theme of nature
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,as it applies to\NHoofcliff's love--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did somepony leave a light on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,OH! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll continue this\Ndiscussion when I get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:01:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\Nby YayPonies\NWe have muffins!\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.18,0:01:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were called\Ntoo! Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so much better\Ngoing with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was about to come and get\Nyou but then I got distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since the\Nmap called us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing a\Nton of research.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Testing out potential\Nfriendship problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,diversifying my\Nsolution portfolio...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ever since the map called us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But that happened\Nfive minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but I want to be one\Nhundred percent prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm the\NPrincess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How would it look if I couldn't\Nsolve a friendship problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so lucky I'm\Nbeing sent with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which,\Nwhere are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Smokey Mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've never\Nbeen there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither have I. And there isn't\Na lot of information on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All I could find was this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Smokey Mountains harbor\Nthe most beautiful valley
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of Equestria between its\Ntwo majestic mountain peaks."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And where there's nature,\Nthere's a ton of animal friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to\Nget started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little nervous, since\Nthat's all I could find.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I usually like to be\Na bit more prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem pretty\Nprepared to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those...for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! I've prepared our things:\NSnacks, books, blankets, books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You said books twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think our friendship\Nproblem's going to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NBut I'm sure we'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it'll be\Na problem about lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll find\Nout when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Could it be about when two\Nfriends just randomly decide
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to do something together\Nbut they forget to invite
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the third friend and the\Nthird friend feels left out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Or where one friend tells\Nanother friend's secret
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,after they ask them not to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll know very, very soon,\Nsince we're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, let me get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I've been a little\Nscidilly-bopty-boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't believe this\Nis finally happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What in\NEquestria is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing like your\Nbook said it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, I'm feeling\Nvery unprepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do we even start?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe by figuring out where the\Nflying pumpkins are coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, hi, hello. Excuse us,\Nbut... what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're pumpkining our neighbors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But, umm, why are you\Npumpkining your neighbors?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because the McColts\Nare just plain rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a tick.\NWho are you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not spies for\Nthe McColts are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Twilight Sparkle, the\NPrincess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am here to solve\Nyour friendship problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Fluttershy. And\Num, I'm here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma Hooffield.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you, but\Nyou're wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have a\Nfriendship problem;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we have a McColt problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's absolutely\Nno friendship there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe there could be if we\Nfigure out what the McColts did
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to make you so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well they've\Ndone so many things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why just today, they shot\Npebbles at our farmhouse
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and wrecked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See, we're not very\Ngood at building
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so all it took was a\Nlittle pebble. But still.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what to do. We're\Ngonna talk with these McColts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and hear their\Nside of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we have all the facts,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we can put an end to this,\Nusing reason and rationale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she's the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, could you\Nplease call off the pumpkining?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Come on, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,State your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably spies\Nfor the Hooffields.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey wait, you're an Alicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought just the three\Nprincesses were Alicorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There are four Alicorn\Nprincesses in Equestria now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Twilight Sparkle, The\NPrincess of Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a new princess?\NWhen did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And, and how did the Hooffields\Ncome by a princess spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not spies! Why does\Neverypony assume we're spies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we don't get a lot of\Nvisitors. I'm Big Daddy McColt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You caught us at a weird time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle\Nof a giant feud
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with our terrible neighbors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually,\Nthat's why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To solve your problem\Nwith the Hooffields.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're here to help\Nus get rid of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what\NI meant at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you ain't for\Nus, you're against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} We are not{\i0}\N{\i1} on anypony's side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here to help you\Nbecome friends again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's gonna be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe we've ever been\Nfriends with the Hooffields.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just really upset\Nyou ruined their farmhouse--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a hog-wogglin'\Nminute! We only did that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because the Hooffields pulled\Nthe pin out of our wagon wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole week's worth of food\Nrollin' down the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Us McColts are\Nmighty fine builders
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but we don't know the\Nfirst thing about farming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to travel a ways\Naway to buy our food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, we'll be stuck\Neating the pumpkins
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the Hooffields launched at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pumpkin bread, pumpkin\Nsoup, pumpkin quesadillas,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,pumpkin paella, pumpkin cheese,\Npumpkin pie, pumpkin fri-ta-tas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually that all sounds\Npretty good, but it'll get old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you tried meeting\Nat a neutral location,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about your problems, and\Nreally listening to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No. They'd sooner\Nlaunch their dinners at us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,than listen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they'll listen to me.\NI'm an impartial third party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention,\NHooffields and McColts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not on anypony's side, but I\Ncan see you're both wasting time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and resources on being\Nmean to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies are supposed to help\Neach other and be kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's stop this\Nsenseless fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There. That should do it.\NReady to go home, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to, but if we've\Nsolved the problem already,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't our cutie\Nmarks be glowing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. They should be\Nglowing any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for potential friendship\Nsolution number twenty-eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we should find\Nout why the Hooffields
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,are launching tomatoes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,One at a time, Greenhoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you smush them\Ntomaters in the slingshot,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,they won't break on the McColts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? I\Nasked you to stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that what you\Nwere hollerin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought the McColts\Nrubbed you the wrong way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so we tomatered them\Nfor ya. My mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the tomater slingshots!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Reload the tomater slingshots!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna paint\Ntheir mountaintop red!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that didn't work.\NI was so sure it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a good plan, but we\Nneed to think of another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This fight is really affecting\Nthe animals around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry. I'll just...find\Nthe root of the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and work from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon us, Ma, but do you\Nremember what started
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,this whole feud in\Nthe first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They know what they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They know what they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to think\Nneither of you know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what either of you have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure we do. Them Hooffields\Ndid us a grave injustice
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,some time ago for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear, hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,O-kay, backup plan\Nto the backup plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can find some common\Nground that you can bond over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do when\Nyou're not fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy. Getting\Nready to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you hope to\Nget out of fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The satisfaction of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of winning what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight, of course. To\Nprove our family is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The best at what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Winning! Haven't\Nyou been listenin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So the only thing they have in\Ncommon is that they both want
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to win a fight and neither\Nof them know what it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I end this feud if I\Ndon't know what it's about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. Maybe somepony just\Nneeds to say they're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And friendship solution\N#48, but we can move it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you\Nagreed to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This apology cake\Nwill go a long way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to making amends\Nbetween you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Which part of my argument\Nchanged your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The part where I said the\Nbenefits of friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,outweigh the cost of war?\NOr the part where I said
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiveness is an\Ninvestment in happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you even\Nlistening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ma Hooffield--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooffield alert! Arm the canons!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,--with an apology cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say...cake? As in, cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider it a gesture of\Ngood will, from us to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had cake in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a beautiful cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of this as more\Nthan just a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first step in the\Nlong road to forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing says let's be friends\Nlike a cake that says
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"let's be friends".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote that in\Nicing on the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,For glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,McColts! Assume delta\Nforce formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma Hooffield! You planted\Nponies in that cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Wait, were you\Nserious about apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why in Equestria\Nwould we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done so\Nmany things wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as many as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could just\Nnot yell so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,or maybe stop saying\Nwords altogether...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Twilight? We should\Nprobably get back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you need\Na break, that's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but I really can't\Ndo this without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if we\Ncan do this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I make things right,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they're just going\Nto fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, little fellas. That's\NOK. You can come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you poor things! There\Nisn't enough food here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Brr! And you're freezing! I'm\Ngonna take you all home with me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and get you all hot cocoas. How\Ndo you feel about book clubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This was supposed to be\Nthe most beautiful valley
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of Equestria.\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! They know what\Nhappened here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! You have to listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,EVERYPONY FREEZE!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, you\Nhave to tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot harder to\Nfreeze an army of ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,than just six of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you keep fighting, there\Nis something you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, there were\Ntwo best friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...Grub Hooffield\Nand Piles McColt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When they found the valley\Nbetween the Smokey Mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,they knew it was\Nsomething special.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So they made a promise to each\Nother to protect and preserve
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the valley for all its\Nadorable furry inhabitants.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But, they disagreed\Non how to go about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Grub wanted to start\Nby planting crops
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so that everypony would\Nhave something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But Piles thought it\Nwould be better to start
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,by building a shelter to protect\Nthem against the cold and wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The two ponies were unable\Nto come to an understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So Piles went ahead and\Nbuilt a shelter anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly where Grub was\Ngoing to start his farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Grub was upset, so he\Ntore down Piles' shelter
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so he could plant his crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They kept fighting,\Nback and forth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,until it turned into a feud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The valley suffered from\Nthe constant destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,until finally the\NHooffields and McColts moved
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to separate mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then, the valley and\Nall the animals in it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,continued to be caught\Nin the crossfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, by fighting, you're\Ndestroying the very thing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that brought you here\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's time you both put\Nyour differences aside
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and come together, if\Nnot for yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then for the sake of these\Ncute and cuddly guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, shucks. We never meant\Nto hurt you little critters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They say they\Naccept your apology!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Princess? You\Ncan unfreeze us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma Hooffield? We promise we\Nwon't fight you no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Us too. Except we\Npromise not to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it doesn't matter\Nwho's right. We're both wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one thing\Nwe can agree on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so proud of you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I would just\Nlike to point out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that I was the first\Nto admit I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be, but I promised\Nnot to fight first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That counts for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right. We don't\Nhave to speak animal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to know what y'all\Nare sayin'. Truce?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo-wee, ain't that\Na pretty sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The McColts are going to\Nhelp us rebuild our homes --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,good ones this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Hooffields are going\Nto help us grow some crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not pumpkins!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for teaching us that\Nfriendship is so much better
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,than winning a silly argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! I told you\Nwe'd figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We did. And we didn't need my\Nfriendship portfolio to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We just needed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you think\Nwill happen next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all been called\Nby the map now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll find\Nout when we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it summons all six\Nof us to another place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Or another pony we\Nweren't expecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it wants us to solve\Nother kinds of problems like
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,quantum physics or why the apple\Ndoesn't fall far from the tree?
